# Planning and subagent accountability

When drafting or updating an implementation plan, include **Subagent reports and follow-ups** when a specialist agent applies or was used (security, FOSS, refactor, Decky debugger, etc.). Summarize findings, cite `.cursor/agents/SUBAGENT_REPORTS.md` (Report log) and/or `docs/security-audit-report.md`, `docs/foss-advocate-report.md` when those are the canonical snapshots.

Before closing risky work (RPC, logging, permissions, large refactors), state triage vs deferred follow-up.
